<body>
    <h1>20260624 - GBO Batch Transition</h1>
    <div class=3D"Section1">
        <p local-id=3D"f7a3f0154a4c"><a class=3D"external-link" data-card-a=
ppearance=3D"inline" href=3D"https://mfc.sharepoint.com/:p:/r/sites/ets-jap=
an/Program%20Delivery/Lapu-Lapu/06_Batch_GBO/PPTs/BatchOpsTransition_v1.ppt=
x?d=3Dwf3ae4fa42dfd46078aa5973ec6bb5101&amp;csf=3D1&amp;web=3D1&amp;e=3D0LA=
sYZ" local-id=3D"f716ba694c9f" rel=3D"nofollow">https://mfc.sharepoint.com/=
:p:/r/sites/ets-japan/Program%20Delivery/Lapu-Lapu/06_Batch_GBO/PPTs/BatchO=
psTransition_v1.pptx?d=3Dwf3ae4fa42dfd46078aa5973ec6bb5101&amp;csf=3D1&amp;=
web=3D1&amp;e=3D0LAsYZ</a></p>
<h1 local-id=3D"d06fd85917c2" id=3D"id-20260624-GBOBatchTransition-GBOJapan=
BatchTransition=E2=80=93LevelSet&amp;ExecutionPlan"><strong>GBO Japan Batch=
 Transition =E2=80=93 Level Set &amp; Execution Plan</strong></h1>
<h2 local-id=3D"f7ce0753f94b" id=3D"id-20260624-GBOBatchTransition-1.Object=
ive"><strong>1. Objective</strong></h2>
<p local-id=3D"9d6eecc6bf20">Align stakeholders on an <strong>executable tr=
ansition plan</strong> to migrate Japan batch operations into a <strong>GBO=
-owned 24x7 operating model</strong>, with a <strong>September pilot valida=
ting end-to-end ownership</strong>.</p>
<hr local-id=3D"e318e727-a77a-4f00-9064-c11b97c52c20">
<h2 local-id=3D"9e63dddcbe1a" id=3D"id-20260624-GBOBatchTransition-2.Target=
OperatingModel"><strong>2. Target Operating Model</strong></h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"9decb55eaa02" id=3D"id-20260624-GBOBatchTransition-Operatin=
gPrinciples"><strong>Operating Principles</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"2f06d971-2aac-476b-b292-fa57d89b4d12">
<li local-id=3D"a6bfaefb-26dd-43e3-a11a-8cad604b27f4">
<p local-id=3D"3f4ae2187265">Centralized <strong>GBO execution of batch wor=
kloads (24x7)</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3028ec37-8284-4605-92cf-732dabe272ba">
<p local-id=3D"78fa3994ba99">Japan teams shift from <strong>execution =E2=
=86=92 stability, input management, and failure prevention</strong></p></li=
>
<li local-id=3D"396fdedc-6151-4613-a915-64dd4973eabe">
<p local-id=3D"663d9f4a38df">Strict enforcement: <strong>No runbook =3D No =
onboarding</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8927998d-cc1a-48b5-ae6d-2a93f6072e13">
<p local-id=3D"fc6ccb1f1875">Full alignment with <strong>Lapu-Lapu global o=
perating model (standardization, observability, governance)</strong></p></l=
i>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"978ab5d54ad6" id=3D"id-20260624-GBOBatchTransition-Roles&am=
p;Responsibilities"><strong>Roles &amp; Responsibilities</strong></h3>
<div class=3D"table-wrap">
<table data-layout=3D"default" data-local-id=3D"624d77c9-f04a-4e66-9e56-fe5=
5f60d949e" class=3D"confluenceTable">
<tbody>
<tr data-local-id=3D"06afe1c8-7ab5-4ac2-9d0a-90aacafc89e3">
<th data-local-id=3D"9a654458-338e-43c9-9aeb-1d90b50ea624" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"c6f8f495d727">Team</p></th>
<th data-local-id=3D"06a8122f-3c2e-480a-91b7-bf1db5192101" class=3D"conflue=
nceTh">
<p local-id=3D"2a4cd383b996">Responsibility</p></th>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"66f2e27b-7594-4888-b87a-b08a8434d2e7">
<td data-local-id=3D"1b4ec40c-75c4-46c0-a4a5-baf2d57b1995" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"63fe9d05ddcc">Japan Application Teams</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"ee4a7d90-6224-4c59-965a-f79004b307c3" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"9f0d7a9e0457">Provide accurate job inputs, runbooks, and req=
uests</p></td>
</tr>
<tr data-local-id=3D"94ece012-c2cc-48f5-9202-198e0893ee2e">
<td data-local-id=3D"48d865a5-78e8-4b80-8308-6bc02aab23f4" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"c5c846926acb">GBO</p></td>
<td data-local-id=3D"11b94d08-64f9-4c9e-b555-555a1bbd8b24" class=3D"conflue=
nceTd">
<p local-id=3D"cd442e05c178">24x7 execution, monitoring, escalation, govern=
ance</p></td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"eb9096fa-d104-47b4-b446-c5ce415ce7d8">
<h2 local-id=3D"aff71a4d5c7e" id=3D"id-20260624-GBOBatchTransition-3.ScopeD=
efinition"><strong>3. Scope Definition</strong></h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"8a9c005f3527" id=3D"id-20260624-GBOBatchTransition-InScope(=
Phase1)"><strong>In Scope (Phase 1)</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"72cc109d-838b-4dad-a10f-50167ad39f34">
<li local-id=3D"f5fc0479-6b3a-439d-810c-fd593fe1bed0">
<p local-id=3D"e7ab00aa99c6"><strong>CA batch jobs (primary focus)</strong>=
 for standardized onboarding</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"560ef484-9f49-4908-988b-1180c9f70a17">
<p local-id=3D"eec12b4e9c6c"><strong>Test environment front-system batch op=
erations</strong> (MLK, SCV, AGW, SSW, PAweb, WFI, BPM)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3357c433-7ca9-4332-a7b1-6a6111245311">
<p local-id=3D"f83235d3b0db"><strong>L0/L1 operational activities</strong> =
(repeatable, request-driven workload)</p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"ed6748aa1c89" id=3D"id-20260624-GBOBatchTransition-To-BeTra=
nsitionScope"><strong>To-Be Transition Scope</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"c5514305-8edb-462b-8209-24b9b14edcc3">
<li local-id=3D"072f5da1-76d6-404b-8421-42eaf7ded5b1">
<p local-id=3D"1f743beebef9">Batch execution (test environments initially)<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dcccd5fb-a7b5-4feb-ac64-f185dce47435">
<p local-id=3D"06c8924dd023">Ad-hoc batch request handling</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dcc1c4b5-141c-4fd3-b44c-807f8e1a6811">
<p local-id=3D"340c21ffe39b">Input validation &amp; prerequisite checks</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"a5642a44-db4c-4f7f-b239-213a1152e828">
<p local-id=3D"7c9c20bbfa97">Execution monitoring &amp; reporting</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cefbc248-4ad4-41c8-b265-897f851cb3bc">
<p local-id=3D"a661cf738987">Output coordination with downstream systems</p=
></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"5eb2488fd701" id=3D"id-20260624-GBOBatchTransition-OutofSco=
pe/RequiresAssessment"><strong>Out of Scope / Requires Assessment</strong><=
/h3>
<ul local-id=3D"61227e58-11c9-474f-b4e4-93dd2e18215f">
<li local-id=3D"040ed351-64d3-4f2d-a15d-efb85e29d385">
<p local-id=3D"7b6c56d7fdb1">Manual and non-CA jobs (require inventory + re=
adiness validation)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"845aeab7-426b-402f-b9fa-d4f9dbbdc031">
<h2 local-id=3D"b5865fafa280" id=3D"id-20260624-GBOBatchTransition-4.Curren=
tStatevsTargetState"><strong>4. Current State vs Target State</strong></h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"b472904c29b0" id=3D"id-20260624-GBOBatchTransition-Current(=
As-Is)"><strong>Current (As-Is)</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"8abce5a1-93e1-4a8a-8e89-93b718e69d21">
<li local-id=3D"ff91fcf7-ed38-441e-928c-84ee2d7cc740">
<p local-id=3D"41e1b397da33">Execution-heavy workload handled by engineerin=
g teams</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"aa275531-cd26-4c69-9ecb-91a094d01cb6">
<p local-id=3D"bcd5d52829b1">Manual processes with <strong>no standardized =
runbooks</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e7966a59-4dcb-4c9d-b6ea-641d8c779dcb">
<p local-id=3D"c4816b1a858d">High reliance on <strong>individual SME knowle=
dge</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0681c98c-f7ad-40be-8ae3-13743c16d4c5">
<p local-id=3D"59869c59afa8">Limited monitoring and centralized visibility<=
/p></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"d0d44d1b1489" id=3D"id-20260624-GBOBatchTransition-Target(T=
o-Be)"><strong>Target (To-Be)</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"150ce175-f6ca-456a-9873-30cce02fb29e">
<li local-id=3D"f542dd37-1699-47a9-95bd-36d6d1612846">
<p local-id=3D"a7bee4860b10">Fully <strong>centralized execution under GBO<=
/strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"adc709f3-2d7d-4a72-877b-96bc38cee480">
<p local-id=3D"d5efb113785a"><strong>Runbook-driven operations with automat=
ion enablement</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0f68414c-0520-4759-93de-4e4dbbd58379">
<p local-id=3D"c7a9dd833b84">Integrated <strong>monitoring + observability<=
/strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6841ecf4-5015-4b4c-91b1-c6fd42923baf">
<p local-id=3D"8c6cf10f6b52">Reduced reliance on SMEs, improved auditabilit=
y</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"1e3bf0c2-2640-42f0-b72c-5da4fa73dbba">
<h2 local-id=3D"95db419eda03" id=3D"id-20260624-GBOBatchTransition-5.Execut=
ionPlan(WorkBreakdownStructure)"><strong>5. Execution Plan (Work Breakdown =
Structure)</strong></h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"217a1acc1d0a" id=3D"id-20260624-GBOBatchTransition-WP1:Oper=
atingModelDefinition"><strong>WP1: Operating Model Definition</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"d42530a6-23be-4ff8-b086-8e5c90fb2095">
<li local-id=3D"cdff2c7c-9ecc-4151-836f-e2994da23ffa">
<p local-id=3D"1dd7017f7a54">Define GBO <strong>24x7 execution model and sc=
ope boundaries</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b4602e00-9ba4-4fc7-b7a6-b34f32f1a4ff">
<p local-id=3D"d5b262866808">Establish <strong>execution vs requestor respo=
nsibilities (RACI)</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"80fdac30-1a01-4a98-8374-8174c4beb787">
<p local-id=3D"727dc2d71be3">Define SLO categories:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"aeed5d48-fcff-43cf-a1b1-1c0a69433e4a">
<li local-id=3D"851bf83e-ddfc-487c-ac8b-8261e466b8a0">
<p local-id=3D"f6c4ad5093ad">Scheduled batch</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b4431f86-541a-4bf1-99ea-1105c8119751">
<p local-id=3D"e2c686375100">Ad-hoc batch</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c06370ab-059f-4c91-966e-857d0bd85778">
<p local-id=3D"81e88581b8c4">Incident recovery</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"a43f6bde-9eae-40ef-9c33-b31b7a1be36b">
<p local-id=3D"57a634e9a1d2">Define escalation flow (GBO =E2=86=92 L3)</p><=
/li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"7eee0d4a-cadd-4d4c-8321-c9585a975a30">
<h3 local-id=3D"e68ab86f6de5" id=3D"id-20260624-GBOBatchTransition-WP2:Inve=
ntoryBaseline"><strong>WP2: Inventory Baseline</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"bc92f648-377c-4ecc-9d3c-51adc21a4211">
<li local-id=3D"afa82f9c-7c1e-4a6f-a966-991238444439">
<p local-id=3D"bc708196326b">Consolidate <strong>complete CA job inventory<=
/strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2af68458-d12e-4bc4-b0cf-4926219f08e9">
<p local-id=3D"b88b5a5095bd">Identify:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"753df15d-ffd0-4558-a55c-a9e0e585caa3">
<li local-id=3D"46281daa-dec3-498a-8083-67ad077139b7">
<p local-id=3D"d781f9420bf3">Non-CA jobs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"65cd49fc-e6ef-435d-b313-707a8442d976">
<p local-id=3D"4cc2bce9cc7b">Manual/script-driven jobs</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"11f77c70-86c8-4420-9032-6b24e975c80b">
<p local-id=3D"0e1f22217529">Map:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"55ce3e3b-01b7-4f04-8b56-20f1e6641997">
<li local-id=3D"acdbe1eb-0e1b-4b3e-bd15-cd59a561ae8d">
<p local-id=3D"9397629c1ca0">Ownership</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8c5d32d5-7996-4abf-aaea-0bcbf2cabcee">
<p local-id=3D"830cc00db7d1">Execution dependencies</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"1923a771-ad77-478a-9c85-597d568f1091">
<p local-id=3D"5d65a55d07e4">Capture failure patterns and incident history<=
br>
=E2=86=92 Output: <strong>Complete batch landscape view</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"4eb56500-6c97-4259-b89e-db9e2de55291">
<h3 local-id=3D"d0f599c9c0a0" id=3D"id-20260624-GBOBatchTransition-WP3:Runb=
ookStandardization"><strong>WP3: Runbook Standardization</strong></h3>
<ul local-id=3D"150e64db-3bfe-4705-960f-9c4b47c11632">
<li local-id=3D"67a784ad-ad6c-4371-a2f5-b2aee45a70db">
<p local-id=3D"9eea492cb95a">Define <strong>standard runbook template (L1/L=
2/L3 aligned)</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1bd4365e-53a4-4b46-b2df-260648cd3a1d">
<p local-id=3D"94eb5e8306e5">Convert existing documentation into:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"76372579-595b-4141-b3c2-831a7c76d2ea">
<li local-id=3D"eb551497-efc5-4060-9f16-41a9a0d3e660">
<p local-id=3D"0509158da449">Step-by-step execution flows</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4b820413-25f7-405b-aeaf-0e02f149bbd7">
<p local-id=3D"12aec59a680d">Troubleshooting paths</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2b349d28-1f20-4ae2-aa67-b198b9fa30db">
<p local-id=3D"81c255cd3a48">Escalation triggers</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"b8bdac1b-00af-41b7-a99b-41255a24c314">
<p local-id=3D"da452ccad68f">Validate:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"0e484a0b-210d-4c1f-9699-5f082fbfa532">
<li local-id=3D"9658048d-f187-4438-a21c-e052f40c1feb">
<p local-id=3D"4cd3d2f44e85">Completeness</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"31c25e6f-18b1-44a5-801f-429d8fd8f04d">
